26#pragma once
27
28#include "ActiveDOMObject.h"
29#include "CacheStorageConnection.h"
30#include "FetchRequest.h"
31#include "FetchResponse.h"
32#include <wtf/UniqueRef.h>
33
34namespace WebCore {
35
36class ScriptExecutionContext;
37
38class DOMCache final : public RefCounted<DOMCache>, public ActiveDOMObject {
39public:
40 static Ref<DOMCache> create(ScriptExecutionContext& context, String&& name, uint64_t identifier, Ref<CacheStorageConnection>&& connection) { return adoptRef(*new DOMCache(context, WTFMove(name), identifier, WTFMove(connection))); }
41 ~DOMCache();
42
43 using RequestInfo = FetchRequest::Info;
44
45 using KeysPromise = DOMPromiseDeferred<IDLSequence<IDLInterface<FetchRequest>>>;
46
47 void match(RequestInfo&&, CacheQueryOptions&&, Ref<DeferredPromise>&&);
48
49 using MatchAllPromise = DOMPromiseDeferred<IDLSequence<IDLInterface<FetchResponse>>>;
50 void matchAll(std::optional<RequestInfo>&&, CacheQueryOptions&&, MatchAllPromise&&);
51 void add(RequestInfo&&, DOMPromiseDeferred<void>&&);
52
53 void addAll(Vector<RequestInfo>&&, DOMPromiseDeferred<void>&&);
54 void put(RequestInfo&&, Ref<FetchResponse>&&, DOMPromiseDeferred<void>&&);
55 void remove(RequestInfo&&, CacheQueryOptions&&, DOMPromiseDeferred<IDLBoolean>&&);
56 void keys(std::optional<RequestInfo>&&, CacheQueryOptions&&, KeysPromise&&);
57
58 const String& name() const { return m_name; }
59 uint64_t identifier() const { return m_identifier; }
60
61 using MatchCallback = CompletionHandler<void(ExceptionOr<RefPtr<FetchResponse>>)>;
62 void doMatch(RequestInfo&&, CacheQueryOptions&&, MatchCallback&&);
63
64 CacheStorageConnection& connection() { return m_connection.get(); }
65
66private:
67 DOMCache(ScriptExecutionContext&, String&& name, uint64_t identifier, Ref<CacheStorageConnection>&&);
68
69 ExceptionOr<Ref<FetchRequest>> requestFromInfo(RequestInfo&&, bool ignoreMethod);
70
71 // ActiveDOMObject
72 void stop() final;
73 const char* activeDOMObjectName() const final;
74
75 void putWithResponseData(DOMPromiseDeferred<void>&&, Ref<FetchRequest>&&, Ref<FetchResponse>&&, ExceptionOr<RefPtr<SharedBuffer>>&&);
76
77 enum class ShouldRetrieveResponses : bool { No, Yes };
78 using RecordsCallback = CompletionHandler<void(ExceptionOr<Vector<DOMCacheEngine::Record>>&&)>;
79 void queryCache(ResourceRequest&&, const CacheQueryOptions&, ShouldRetrieveResponses, RecordsCallback&&);
80
81 void batchDeleteOperation(const FetchRequest&, CacheQueryOptions&&, CompletionHandler<void(ExceptionOr<bool>&&)>&&);
82 void batchPutOperation(const FetchRequest&, FetchResponse&, DOMCacheEngine::ResponseBody&&, CompletionHandler<void(ExceptionOr<void>&&)>&&);
83 void batchPutOperation(Vector<DOMCacheEngine::Record>&&, CompletionHandler<void(ExceptionOr<void>&&)>&&);
84
85 Vector<Ref<FetchResponse>> cloneResponses(const Vector<DOMCacheEngine::Record>&);
86 DOMCacheEngine::Record toConnectionRecord(const FetchRequest&, FetchResponse&, DOMCacheEngine::ResponseBody&&);
87
88 String m_name;
89 uint64_t m_identifier;
90 Ref<CacheStorageConnection> m_connection;
91
92 bool m_isStopped { false };
93};
94
95} // namespace WebCore
